<template>
 <winWheel :segments="items"></winWheel>
</template>

<script>
import winWheel from 'vue-winwheel'

export default {
  name: "sss-ss",
  components: {
    winWheel: winWheel
  },
  data() {
    return {
      items: [
        {
          text: "hola",
          desc:
            "You receive a personalized drawing of the hero of your choice from the one and only Sam `thepladpirate` Wendel.",
        },
        {
          text: "mano",
          desc:
            "Fulfill your lifelong dream of having one of your games hype-casted by one of the WLD team! Just provide the match ID, date and time and watch for the Youtube link to appear in the Discord.",
        },
        {
          text: "como estas",
          desc:
            "Enjoy the groans of sorrow as you select one of the WLD team and the hero you want he (or she) to play. Match ID and date/time will be provided post-match.",
        },
      ],
    };
  }
};
</script>
